Possible Cause 
 The ambient temperature is high. 
The battery terminal is not tightened.
 Procedure 
 Restore the temperature to normal and check whether the alarm is cleared. If yes, no further action is required. Replace the battery temperature sensor with a new one and check whether the alarm is cleared. If yes, no further action is required. Replace the battery with a new one and check whether the alarm is cleared. If yes, no further action is required.
